         <abstract>
            <p>The <foreign xml:lang="gez">Ḥamara nafs</foreign> is a treatise dealing mainly with the birth and nature of Jesus Christ and monophysite doctrine. 
            It is transmitted in the codex unicus <ref type="mss" corresp="BNFet119"/>
            together with <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1386Fekkar"/>, <ref type="work" corresp="LIT1885Marsam"/> and <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2635Dawana"/>. 
         </p>
